# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Retina — Local Environment Overrides
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  These values override secrets from Vault and vault/.env.
#  Only add variables you want to change for local development.
#
#  To use:  cp .env.example .env
#
#  Resolution order (first wins):
#    1. process.env (manual env vars)
#    2. This file (.env)
#    3. Vault service
#    4. Shared vault/.env fallback
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RETINA_PORT="3333"

# ── Vault Connection ──────────────────────────────────────────
# VAULT_SERVICE_URL="http://192.168.86.2:5599"
# VAULT_SERVICE_TOKEN=""

# ── Prism (AI Gateway) ───────────────────────────────────────
# PRISM_URL="http://localhost:7777"
# PRISM_WS_URL="ws://localhost:7777"

# ── Tools API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TOOLS_API_URL="http://localhost:5590"
# MINIO_PUBLIC_URL=""
